@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h3>@ViewData["Title"]</h3>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
        h3 {
            color: #d9850f;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: justify;
        }



        strong {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #d9480f;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>

    <ul>
        This Privacy Policy outlines the types of personal information collected by our Pet Clinic Application, specifically concerning vaccine-related data, and how we use, maintain, and protect that information.
        <li>
            <strong>Information We Collect</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal Information: When you use our Pet Clinic Application, we may collect personal information such as your name, surname, and pet-related details (e.g., pet's name, age, and vaccines).</li>
                <li>Vaccine Information: We collect data related to your pet's vaccination history, including vaccine type.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>How We Use Your Information</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Providing Veterinary Services: We use the information collected to provide veterinary services, including administering vaccines.</li>
                <li>Vaccine Reminders: We may use your pet's vaccine history to send you timely reminders for upcoming vaccinations or boosters to ensure your pet's health and compliance with vaccination schedules.</li>
                <li>Improving User Experience: We may analyze vaccine-related data and usage patterns to understand pet owners' needs and preferences, improve our services, and enhance the user experience of our application.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Data Security</strong>
            <p>We are committed to protecting the security of your personal information, including vaccine-related data. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard your data against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Data Sharing</strong>
            <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information, including vaccine-related data, to third parties without your consent, except as required by law or necessary for providing our services. However, we may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our application, conducting business, or servicing you.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Data Retention</strong>
            <p>We retain personal information, including vaccine records, for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Changes to This Privacy Policy</strong>
            <p>We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Your continued use of our Pet Clinic Application after any modifications indicates your acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.</p>
        </li>
        </br>
    </ul>

</body>
</html>

